WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 21]

01:45.040 --> 01:46.290
The rain is bound to fall.

01:46.950 --> 01:48.330
I'm bound to be wed.

01:49.150 --> 01:50.380
Trees are ready to bloom.

01:51.200 --> 01:52.410
I'm ready to be married.

01:53.280 --> 01:55.130
Flowers long to bear fruit.

01:55.220 --> 01:56.480
[Tales of a Mortal Dream]

01:56.480 --> 01:57.540
I long to be married.

01:57.540 --> 01:59.900
[Su Jian]

02:01.430 --> 02:02.100
Is this

02:02.840 --> 02:04.100
the Little Pomegranate from the painting?

02:07.000 --> 02:08.180
So we are in...

02:10.400 --> 02:11.300
I was just thinking.

02:12.560 --> 02:13.470
This painting must carry

02:13.470 --> 02:14.900
the artist's memories and emotions.

02:16.190 --> 02:16.810
Maybe

02:17.400 --> 02:19.090
I could try the spell Master left me,

02:19.470 --> 02:21.060
like entering the Star Stone illusion.

02:21.630 --> 02:22.690
I didn't expect it to actually work.

02:23.520 --> 02:25.690
Cui Jun is good-looking.

02:26.520 --> 02:28.900
We've known each other since childhood and have been betrothed before birth.

02:29.400 --> 02:30.180
Cui Jun...

02:30.680 --> 02:31.460
The painter is

02:31.900 --> 02:32.770
Cui...

02:33.520 --> 02:34.440
Cui Jun?

02:34.800 --> 02:35.720
The one who painted this.

02:35.720 --> 02:36.990
But I've always treated him

02:37.240 --> 02:39.060
like a younger brother.

02:39.060 --> 02:40.350
How can anyone

02:40.350 --> 02:42.180
marry their own brother?

02:42.190 --> 02:43.530
Does that make any sense?

02:43.530 --> 02:45.210
Is that even reasonable?

02:46.000 --> 02:47.900
A forced melon is never sweet.

02:48.750 --> 02:49.420
Better let it rot

02:51.430 --> 02:52.620
on the vine.

02:55.910 --> 02:56.930
When

02:57.150 --> 02:58.140
will I ever

02:58.470 --> 03:00.210
have a love

03:00.630 --> 03:01.210
like in the stories?

03:02.400 --> 03:03.740
He chases, I run.

03:03.960 --> 03:05.490
I tease, he laughs.

03:05.840 --> 03:07.580
I faint, and he kisses me.

03:08.120 --> 03:09.620
How beautiful that must be.

03:12.710 --> 03:14.460
Oh, tree.

03:18.960 --> 03:19.810
Will there

03:20.280 --> 03:22.460
be an attractive, interesting man

03:22.750 --> 03:24.060
who falls in love with me?

03:24.470 --> 03:25.770
If the answer is yes,

03:25.770 --> 03:27.490
stay silent

03:28.030 --> 03:29.340
and don't move, alright?

03:48.080 --> 03:49.020
Handsome,

03:50.560 --> 03:51.530
who are you?

03:52.590 --> 03:54.340
You could get arrested

03:55.360 --> 03:56.930
for breaking into someone's home.

04:00.280 --> 04:01.060
I'm kind.

04:01.630 --> 04:02.370
I won't make a fuss over this.

04:02.910 --> 04:03.970
You should leave now.

04:04.430 --> 04:05.420
If fate allows,

04:05.840 --> 04:07.460
we may meet again someday.

04:08.750 --> 04:09.930
Go on.

04:10.430 --> 04:11.970
Hurry and leave.

04:13.120 --> 04:14.800
Don't get too mesmerized by my beauty,

04:14.800 --> 04:15.650
alright?

04:19.070 --> 04:19.810
Not leaving?

04:23.240 --> 04:24.780
So you want to stay and have a chat?

04:42.040 --> 04:42.890
Sir,

04:43.720 --> 04:45.100
sneaking up

04:45.240 --> 04:46.330
behind a lady

04:46.330 --> 04:47.980
and eavesdropping on her

04:48.240 --> 04:49.420
is a no-no.

04:49.430 --> 04:50.300
A little naughty.

04:52.160 --> 04:53.060
Tell me.

04:53.560 --> 04:54.370
From which line

04:54.430 --> 04:56.010
did you start listening?

04:56.430 --> 04:57.130
Was it

04:57.560 --> 04:58.570
"He chases, I run",

04:58.870 --> 05:01.540
or "I faint, and he kisses me"?

05:08.630 --> 05:10.060
The way you greet people

05:10.060 --> 05:10.930
is rather unique.

05:11.270 --> 05:13.930
You've definitely caught my attention.

05:15.720 --> 05:16.690
I'm Su Jian.

05:17.000 --> 05:18.100
What's your name?

05:18.390 --> 05:19.620
Where do you live?

05:19.950 --> 05:20.890
How old are you?

05:21.160 --> 05:21.930
Are you married?

05:22.190 --> 05:23.740
Have you picked names for our children yet?

05:24.830 --> 05:25.490
You're tired?

05:26.950 --> 05:28.330
The sky is still bright.

05:29.630 --> 05:30.540
No rush.

05:31.160 --> 05:32.100
How do I undo this?

05:32.830 --> 05:33.370
How...

05:33.680 --> 05:34.060
Help me.

05:35.160 --> 05:36.130
Sir.

05:37.360 --> 05:38.690
Why won't you speak?

05:39.630 --> 05:41.250
I often come to this weaving house,

05:41.800 --> 05:43.220
but I've never seen you before.

05:48.560 --> 05:49.620
Where are you going?

05:50.040 --> 05:51.420
It's raining outside.

05:51.680 --> 05:53.100
For a handsome man like you,

05:53.120 --> 05:54.370
if your clothes get soaked,

05:54.430 --> 05:55.690
you should take them off immediately

05:58.510 --> 05:59.220
and dry them,

06:00.390 --> 06:01.450
or you'll fall ill.

06:06.310 --> 06:06.860
So it's true.

06:08.310 --> 06:09.490
Han Ba can't speak.

06:11.720 --> 06:12.450
Wangyan.

06:14.720 --> 06:15.370
Wangyan.

06:16.310 --> 06:16.930
Jian.

06:22.120 --> 06:23.980
Si Feng once told me

06:25.160 --> 06:26.810
I had carried out a mission alone

06:26.950 --> 06:28.250
involving Han Ba.

06:29.390 --> 06:30.420
Could this be that mission?

06:31.630 --> 06:32.250
Mission?

06:34.190 --> 06:35.780
Disguising yourself as Su Jian's sister?

06:39.430 --> 06:40.980
Looks like you've cast the Word Magic

06:41.360 --> 06:42.780
over the entire Su family.

06:43.390 --> 06:45.100
Su Jian really believes you're her sister.

06:46.750 --> 06:48.420
Wangyan, you made iced treats again?

06:49.000 --> 06:49.800
How can you make ice treats

06:49.800 --> 06:51.130
in any season?

06:51.680 --> 06:53.300
Do you know magic?

06:54.160 --> 06:55.740
You must be the fairy

06:55.950 --> 06:57.420
from the stories.

06:58.360 --> 06:58.980
Is it good?

06:59.720 --> 07:00.980
I remember you once said

07:01.560 --> 07:03.250
you liked making iced treats for Lu Wuyi.

07:04.160 --> 07:04.740
It seems

07:05.510 --> 07:07.180
you've brought your real habits

07:07.750 --> 07:08.690
into the mission.

07:09.510 --> 07:10.660
Aren't you afraid of exposing yourself?

07:11.720 --> 07:13.490
You must've known

07:13.950 --> 07:15.330
I was troubled,

07:15.950 --> 07:17.420
so you made these iced treats

07:17.630 --> 07:19.250
to comfort me.

07:20.600 --> 07:21.690
What are you talking about?

07:22.360 --> 07:23.660
Lotus seeds.

07:24.480 --> 07:25.980
I'm as pitiful as these lotus seeds.

07:26.560 --> 07:27.450
My heart

07:27.950 --> 07:30.300
is like these iced lotus seeds.

07:30.600 --> 07:33.220
Col' an' bitter...

07:33.630 --> 07:34.860
Are you speaking in tongues?

07:35.310 --> 07:36.490
Cold

07:36.950 --> 07:38.810
and bitter.

07:40.480 --> 07:42.100
I know what you mean.

07:42.630 --> 07:43.740
It's been a whole month,

07:44.510 --> 07:46.250
and you're still not over

07:46.270 --> 07:47.130
that mute man?

07:47.240 --> 07:50.100
What? Mute?

07:50.510 --> 07:51.820
Wangyan, you're so ugly,

07:51.820 --> 07:52.420
but why do you speak so...

07:53.750 --> 07:55.310
I mean, you're so pretty,

07:55.310 --> 07:57.060
but why do you speak harshly?

07:57.630 --> 08:00.060
He's just steady and quiet.

08:01.000 --> 08:02.220
He complements me.

08:02.830 --> 08:03.890
Is he good-looking?

08:04.390 --> 08:05.100
Of course.

08:05.720 --> 08:06.890
Indeed, you complement each other.

08:08.830 --> 08:09.930
That's an insult.

08:10.190 --> 08:11.860
You really deserve a scolding.

08:12.270 --> 08:13.220
Do you remember

08:13.360 --> 08:14.430
you're supposed to marry Jun

08:14.430 --> 08:15.740
in three months?

08:16.040 --> 08:16.660
Jun?

08:17.190 --> 08:18.250
Who is that?

08:18.360 --> 08:19.570
Chenjun?

08:20.120 --> 08:21.250
Cui Jun.

08:23.560 --> 08:25.810
I don't want to marry him anymore.

08:30.070 --> 08:32.380
Cold and bitter.

08:34.600 --> 08:36.260
You're here brooding over it,

08:36.750 --> 08:38.020
while he can't even

08:38.550 --> 08:39.660
be bothered with you.

08:43.790 --> 08:45.020
They say in stories

08:45.550 --> 08:47.210
that when a woman pursues a man, it's like a thin veil between them.

08:47.750 --> 08:49.360
I've even gone as far

08:49.360 --> 08:50.380
as the barn next door.

08:51.000 --> 08:51.900
I refuse to believe

08:52.600 --> 08:53.970
I can't tear through this thin veil.

08:55.120 --> 08:55.810
Wangyan,

08:56.630 --> 08:57.810
just watch me.

09:04.670 --> 09:05.300
Wangyan.

09:06.600 --> 09:07.300
I choked myself.

09:11.200 --> 09:12.140
If

09:12.480 --> 09:13.970
you still won't speak,

09:14.120 --> 09:15.310
I'll show you

09:15.310 --> 09:16.380
what a fierce woman

09:16.840 --> 09:18.170
is like.

09:22.630 --> 09:23.090
Fine.

09:23.390 --> 09:25.060
I'll smash my head right here and die.

09:25.440 --> 09:26.260
Let's see

09:26.440 --> 09:28.380
if you'll call a physician for me then.

09:54.670 --> 09:55.450
This is a gift for you.

09:56.000 --> 09:57.060
You've barely passed twenty,

09:57.320 --> 09:59.210
it's the perfect age to carry an old man's fan.

10:00.270 --> 10:02.180
Honestly, I was worried you're too handsome,

10:02.670 --> 10:04.090
and other girls might start eyeing you.

10:05.030 --> 10:06.140
This old man's fan

10:06.480 --> 10:07.730
will do just the trick.

10:07.750 --> 10:09.810
It'll make your lofty, noble charm

10:10.080 --> 10:11.690
a little questionable

10:12.200 --> 10:14.500
and make you less appealing to other women.

10:18.240 --> 10:19.420
I've given you a gift.

10:19.790 --> 10:21.090
Won't you at least say thank you?

10:31.790 --> 10:32.730
My name is Su Jian.

10:33.200 --> 10:34.420
What's yours?

10:40.480 --> 10:41.210
You won't even tell me

10:41.240 --> 10:42.810
your name?

10:43.480 --> 10:44.690
If I don't know

10:44.690 --> 10:45.810
your name,

10:46.320 --> 10:47.330
how am I supposed

10:47.330 --> 10:48.060
to match our birth charts

10:48.080 --> 10:49.610
and figure out

10:49.610 --> 10:50.420
when we'll get married?

11:04.750 --> 11:05.730
Do I

11:06.080 --> 11:07.180
look pretty today?

11:08.150 --> 11:09.420
What a delicate flower.

11:09.750 --> 11:11.020
If you don't pick it now,

11:12.000 --> 11:12.810
it might belong

11:15.750 --> 11:17.500
to another man tomorrow.

11:18.000 --> 11:18.420
I...

11:24.380 --> 11:31.220
♪Who granted me this endless pain to wake me from my dream?♪

11:31.540 --> 11:37.980
♪All I want is to close my eyes, wave it all away, and sink into this illusion♪

11:38.700 --> 11:41.860
♪A fleeting soul that caught my eye in this mortal world♪

11:42.180 --> 11:46.060
♪How many hearts still burn so bright?♪

11:46.860 --> 11:51.620
♪I remain guarding this city of bitterness♪

11:52.060 --> 11:58.420
♪Who in this world wrote these cruel, heartless rules?♪

11:58.740 --> 12:05.380
♪That those who wait to reunite are left only with regret?♪

12:06.060 --> 12:09.300
♪Time wears the heart away♪

12:09.460 --> 12:13.580
♪What becomes of longing when the heart is gone?♪

12:14.300 --> 12:18.780
♪A devoted soul chasing the setting sun♪

12:18.790 --> 12:20.540
You always manage to find me.

12:23.390 --> 12:25.140
You always hide in the dark.

12:25.670 --> 12:27.180
Of course no one else can see you.

12:29.240 --> 12:30.450
But I can.

12:30.870 --> 12:32.020
But I can.

12:32.600 --> 12:33.450
My heart.

12:34.320 --> 12:35.060
My heart.

12:35.910 --> 12:37.610
Can feel you are here.

12:51.030 --> 12:52.300
I remember everything now.

12:57.720 --> 12:59.060
But in my memory,

13:00.630 --> 13:02.660
I was saying that to someone else.

13:03.200 --> 13:03.810
Wangyan,

13:05.200 --> 13:05.930
thank you.

13:06.320 --> 13:07.730
You're the only one who can see me.

13:08.910 --> 13:10.810
You always hide in the dark.

13:11.510 --> 13:13.450
Of course no one else can see you,

13:15.440 --> 13:16.420
but I can.

13:17.600 --> 13:18.330
My heart

13:19.960 --> 13:21.660
can feel you're here.

13:27.400 --> 13:28.370
Is it Lu Wuyi?

13:36.720 --> 13:38.090
There's no moon tonight.

13:41.540 --> 13:42.930
The moon is always there.

13:43.910 --> 13:46.020
It's just being mischievous tonight.

13:46.470 --> 13:47.570
It's hiding.

13:48.600 --> 13:50.540
The moon is meant to shine,

13:51.120 --> 13:52.780
to be admired, to be written into poems,

13:53.750 --> 13:55.300
to carry people's longing and praise.

13:56.030 --> 13:57.180
But tonight,

13:57.180 --> 13:58.850
no one can see it.

14:00.440 --> 14:01.450
Will it feel sad?

14:03.790 --> 14:04.610
Jian,

14:06.390 --> 14:07.730
are you talking about yourself?

14:14.750 --> 14:16.090
I am sad.

14:17.630 --> 14:18.330
Wangyan,

14:19.440 --> 14:20.300
you were right.

14:20.630 --> 14:22.500
It's always just been me.

14:23.080 --> 14:24.850
He's never responded to me.

14:25.960 --> 14:28.060
He wouldn't even tell me his name.

14:30.000 --> 14:31.090
He doesn't love you.

14:32.990 --> 14:34.450
But Cui Jun does.

14:34.870 --> 14:35.900
And I love you too.

14:37.670 --> 14:38.930
To me,

14:39.480 --> 14:41.140
you're the most important person.

14:42.440 --> 14:44.330
I'll stay with you forever.

14:45.790 --> 14:46.450
Jian,

14:47.790 --> 14:48.780
sleep.

14:49.670 --> 14:50.660
Have a good dream.

14:51.390 --> 14:53.180
When the dream ends,

14:54.030 --> 14:55.780
I'll wake you.

14:58.480 --> 14:59.690
And if I don't,

15:01.480 --> 15:03.260
don't ever wake up.

15:12.150 --> 15:14.420
Han Ba still refuses to speak.

15:15.630 --> 15:16.210
Jian,

15:17.790 --> 15:18.900
I'm sorry to put you through this.

15:32.720 --> 15:33.300
Wait.

15:39.150 --> 15:40.200
Are you the quiet man

15:40.200 --> 15:41.540
my sister likes?

15:46.750 --> 15:48.060
She suddenly fell ill

15:48.270 --> 15:49.210
and has been unconscious.

15:49.550 --> 15:50.810
The physician said it's a matter of the heart.

15:51.320 --> 15:53.450
Only the voice of the one she loves can bring her back.

16:06.510 --> 16:08.260
I don't have a human name.

16:09.630 --> 16:10.780
I only have a demon name.

16:13.630 --> 16:14.420
I'm Han Ba.

16:15.630 --> 16:16.420
And

16:17.270 --> 16:19.330
the moment I speak,

16:20.000 --> 16:22.380
drought will fall upon the world.

16:24.720 --> 16:26.780
I've lived inside a tree

16:27.960 --> 16:29.180
day after day,

16:30.200 --> 16:31.180
I was so bored.

16:32.670 --> 16:34.380
No one ever spoke to me

16:36.030 --> 16:37.210
until I met you.

16:38.200 --> 16:39.450
Oh, tree.

16:39.600 --> 16:40.540
Will there

16:40.540 --> 16:42.570
be an attractive, interesting man

16:42.600 --> 16:43.810
who falls in love with me?

16:43.810 --> 16:45.450
If the answer is yes,

16:45.750 --> 16:47.610
stay silent

16:49.630 --> 16:50.780
and don't move, alright?

17:02.240 --> 17:03.210
Meeting you

17:04.680 --> 17:07.330
was like a flame melting ice.

17:08.310 --> 17:10.460
This world that was once indifferent to me

17:14.590 --> 17:16.850
suddenly came alive.

17:21.350 --> 17:22.650
Even if I couldn't speak,

17:23.110 --> 17:24.700
just watching you talk

17:26.070 --> 17:27.020
made me happy.

17:31.590 --> 17:33.220
I wanted to answer you.

17:34.310 --> 17:36.410
I wanted to tell you

17:36.920 --> 17:38.060
everything I felt.

17:39.510 --> 17:40.260
But

17:41.440 --> 17:43.300
if I ever responded to your love,

17:44.480 --> 17:46.020
everyone you cherish in this world

17:47.240 --> 17:48.370
would be destroyed by me.

17:54.350 --> 17:56.130
You like stories, don't you?

17:58.030 --> 17:59.090
Stop sleeping.

18:00.310 --> 18:01.410
I'll tell you a story.

18:03.350 --> 18:04.220
Wake up,

18:06.310 --> 18:07.020
alright?

18:22.640 --> 18:23.500
It works.

18:28.240 --> 18:28.980
Jian,

18:29.640 --> 18:31.500
did you hear the voice of the man you love?

18:33.750 --> 18:34.940
The dream is over.

18:36.270 --> 18:37.700
Wake up now.

18:47.550 --> 18:48.300
As expected.

18:48.880 --> 18:50.260
Only the one she loves

18:50.440 --> 18:51.500
could wake her.

18:55.750 --> 18:56.740
This is bad!

18:56.880 --> 18:57.980
- This is bad! - Quiet.

18:57.980 --> 18:58.650
Something's happened!

18:59.240 --> 18:59.890
Su Jian,

18:59.960 --> 19:01.060
why are you still here?

19:01.240 --> 19:02.170
You should go take a look.

19:02.400 --> 19:03.810
Your mother fought someone over water

19:03.830 --> 19:05.130
and was beaten to death.

19:15.680 --> 19:16.810
What was my mission

19:19.200 --> 19:20.130
back then?

19:21.590 --> 19:23.020
Wu Wangyan's mission

19:23.510 --> 19:24.610
was to capture the water demons

19:24.610 --> 19:26.130
hiding in the underground waterways

19:26.480 --> 19:27.740
of Luo'an.

19:28.480 --> 19:29.570
But what does that have to do

19:29.750 --> 19:31.500
with making you speak?

19:32.000 --> 19:32.980
Aren't you supposed to be smart?

19:35.030 --> 19:36.020
Can't you figure that out?

19:36.270 --> 19:37.260
Of course I can.

19:37.350 --> 19:38.700
I just want to hear you say it.

19:40.200 --> 19:41.780
If she wanted to flush out the water demons,

19:43.270 --> 19:45.810
she had to make Han Ba speak, which would trigger a drought,

19:46.680 --> 19:47.940
dry up water sources,

19:48.550 --> 19:49.410
and force the water demons

19:49.680 --> 19:51.980
out of the tangled underground waterways.

19:52.680 --> 19:54.130
There's no way

19:55.110 --> 19:55.960
I would've agreed

19:55.960 --> 19:57.170
to cause such devastation.

19:58.160 --> 19:58.940
That's why

19:59.000 --> 20:00.890
Jiu Ying erased my memory.

20:04.510 --> 20:06.610
Drought brings conflict and unrest.

20:07.830 --> 20:09.780
As fear and hatred multiply,

20:10.070 --> 20:11.460
Jiu Ying feeds on them

20:12.110 --> 20:13.500
and becomes stronger.

20:15.310 --> 20:16.220
I didn't understand back then.

20:18.400 --> 20:19.810
Now I do.

20:21.160 --> 20:23.330
That was Jiu Ying's true intention.

20:30.480 --> 20:31.260
If I didn't speak,

20:32.200 --> 20:33.220
I couldn't save her.

20:35.400 --> 20:36.330
But if I did,

20:37.030 --> 20:38.220
I harmed her

20:39.350 --> 20:40.810
and the entire mortal world.

20:44.350 --> 20:45.540
I don't have a mother anymore.

20:56.030 --> 20:57.650
I know my sins run deep,

20:58.200 --> 20:59.740
but I never dared tell her the truth.

21:01.240 --> 21:01.810
Not until

21:02.590 --> 21:04.500
the double-flower hunter came to bring me to justice.

21:13.350 --> 21:13.980
Han Ba,

21:14.790 --> 21:16.060
you've acted recklessly

21:16.400 --> 21:17.500
and brought drought upon the land,

21:18.270 --> 21:19.810
turning Luo'an into scorched earth,

21:20.400 --> 21:21.540
leaving countless lives in ruin.

21:22.310 --> 21:23.940
By the order of Master Chi Wen,

21:24.200 --> 21:26.060
we're here to take you back to the Shilin Sect to face judgment.

21:26.110 --> 21:27.060
You'd better not try something silly.

21:27.400 --> 21:28.130
My martial senior

21:28.510 --> 21:29.260
is very powerful.

21:31.680 --> 21:32.460
He's getting away.

21:34.310 --> 21:35.570
- I shouldn't have changed my mind... - Si Feng!

21:35.570 --> 21:36.700
...and brought a reckless fool like you along.

21:37.110 --> 21:37.810
Wait outside.

21:37.960 --> 21:38.500
Si Feng!

21:39.350 --> 21:39.980
Si Feng!

21:40.310 --> 21:40.940
Si Feng!

21:41.400 --> 21:42.260
Wait for me.

21:43.000 --> 21:43.920
I'll soon become

21:43.920 --> 21:45.090
a powerful double-flower hunter.

21:46.140 --> 21:46.840
Si Feng,

21:47.270 --> 21:48.090
I finally found you.

21:48.240 --> 21:48.780
Careful!

21:49.240 --> 21:50.020
Careful of what?

21:52.440 --> 21:53.370
I don't want to hurt you.

21:53.440 --> 21:53.850
Stand aside.

21:54.830 --> 21:55.610
I wanted to.

21:56.070 --> 21:56.460
You!

22:01.590 --> 22:02.170
Si Feng,

22:02.270 --> 22:03.060
he's got backup.

22:03.880 --> 22:04.740
Anyway, two against two.

22:05.160 --> 22:05.810
It's even.

22:07.790 --> 22:08.780
Can you even beat her?

22:09.400 --> 22:10.790
She's a thousand-year-old nine-tailed fox

22:10.790 --> 22:12.300
from the Formless Moon Sect.

22:13.070 --> 22:14.060
She's a fox demon?

22:14.680 --> 22:16.070
The double-flower hunter from the Shilin Sect

22:16.070 --> 22:17.460
is quite heartless.

22:18.310 --> 22:19.810
How can you bring yourself

22:20.400 --> 22:22.090
to tear apart a couple in love?

22:23.350 --> 22:24.130
How amusing.

22:24.880 --> 22:26.370
A fox demon from the Formless Moon Sect

22:27.070 --> 22:28.650
lecturing me on human sentiment?

22:29.880 --> 22:31.090
What are you doing here?

22:31.790 --> 22:32.940
I'm here to rid the world

22:33.310 --> 22:34.460
of water demons.

22:35.110 --> 22:37.330
Whether your sect creates evil or destroys it,

22:38.030 --> 22:39.170
can you really tell the difference?

22:40.790 --> 22:41.740
No matter what,

22:42.640 --> 22:44.410
I won't let you take Han Ba away.

22:45.480 --> 22:46.460
The fault isn't his.

22:47.160 --> 22:48.090
He's innocent.

22:48.920 --> 22:49.940
Of course it isn't his fault.

22:50.070 --> 22:50.810
It's yours.

22:51.070 --> 22:52.460
You're the one who made him speak.

22:52.640 --> 22:53.890
You wretched fox.

22:53.960 --> 22:54.980
Don't think you can hide what you did.

22:55.440 --> 22:57.650
I've never sparred with a fox from the Formless Moon Sect.

22:58.110 --> 22:58.850
Today

22:59.400 --> 23:00.460
is the perfect chance.

23:00.750 --> 23:02.300
I've never fought alongside you, Si Feng.

23:02.310 --> 23:04.410
Time to show what I can do.

23:05.240 --> 23:05.780
Wait.

23:08.510 --> 23:10.170
The drought was indeed caused by me.

23:11.440 --> 23:13.650
I'll return to the Shilin Sect with you.

23:15.240 --> 23:15.810
But

23:16.830 --> 23:18.540
let me see her one last time

23:20.720 --> 23:21.890
and bid farewell to her.

23:23.270 --> 23:24.060
Please.

23:34.000 --> 23:34.700
So

23:35.270 --> 23:36.130
you are a demon.

23:38.200 --> 23:40.060
Why did you cause the drought?

23:43.240 --> 23:47.410
The drought killed my mother.

24:08.590 --> 24:09.890
I'll explain everything to Su Jian.

24:11.350 --> 24:12.330
It's not what she thinks.

24:14.550 --> 24:15.540
- It was me. - No need.

24:16.590 --> 24:18.130
I've hurt her enough.

24:20.810 --> 24:22.040
I can't let her know

24:24.350 --> 24:26.370
that the sister she loves was using her all along.

24:27.790 --> 24:28.890
Does the Formless Moon Sect

24:28.960 --> 24:30.480
have Word Magic

24:30.480 --> 24:31.940
that can alter memories?

24:34.270 --> 24:35.850
Can you make her forget me?

24:38.510 --> 24:39.500
Fairy,

24:40.400 --> 24:42.370
aren't your spells powerful?

24:43.510 --> 24:44.810
Can you make me forget him?

24:48.000 --> 24:48.700
Please.

25:24.070 --> 25:24.650
What?

25:25.160 --> 25:26.460
Can't bring yourself to do it?

25:28.000 --> 25:29.300
It's just

25:29.920 --> 25:31.460
their love is rare,

25:32.110 --> 25:33.570
like a precious treasure.

25:34.400 --> 25:35.260
I can't bear to destroy it.

25:42.590 --> 25:43.570
If you can't,

25:44.000 --> 25:45.060
use this.

26:11.270 --> 26:12.610
You've got the softest heart

26:13.480 --> 26:14.650
of any fox I've met.

26:16.480 --> 26:18.170
You left a hope

26:18.920 --> 26:19.850
for Su Jian and Han Ba.

26:34.880 --> 26:36.300
After Su Jian forgot me,

26:36.920 --> 26:38.830
I was ready to return to the Shilin Sect to accept punishment

26:38.830 --> 26:39.700
and end the drought.

26:40.750 --> 26:41.650
But I never expected

26:42.590 --> 26:43.370
Su Jian

26:44.240 --> 26:45.090
to seek revenge on the man

26:45.090 --> 26:46.890
who killed her mother.

26:48.680 --> 26:50.020
She was gravely wounded

26:52.310 --> 26:53.220
and fading fast.

27:03.750 --> 27:05.220
Your spiritual veins will shatter,

27:06.200 --> 27:07.810
and the backlash will destroy you

27:08.680 --> 27:09.810
after pouring your demon power into her.

27:28.030 --> 27:29.220
I only want her

27:30.310 --> 27:31.890
to stay alive

27:33.920 --> 27:35.130
and be happy.

27:57.830 --> 27:59.460
I grew up with Jian.

28:00.830 --> 28:02.020
Marrying her

28:02.880 --> 28:04.540
has always been my greatest wish.

28:06.200 --> 28:07.500
I'll take care of her

28:09.030 --> 28:10.020
for life,

28:10.960 --> 28:11.810
never leave her,

28:12.880 --> 28:13.850
never fail her.

28:16.270 --> 28:17.090
Don't worry.

28:18.440 --> 28:20.090
So Su Jian's fiancé

28:20.310 --> 28:21.780
knew everything all along.

28:22.590 --> 28:24.220
Did Su Jian tell him?

28:26.680 --> 28:27.650
When you truly love someone,

28:29.160 --> 28:30.370
how can any secret stay hidden?

28:31.640 --> 28:32.980
Everything we saw

28:34.640 --> 28:36.220
was Jun's memory.

28:37.340 --> 28:42.780
[Fifty years later]

28:42.780 --> 28:48.460
♪From now on, you'll never grow old♪

28:48.820 --> 28:54.020
♪Even with earth between us, I'll softly sing with you♪

28:56.100 --> 28:59.220
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you...♪

29:00.790 --> 29:02.300
I already know who the person in black is.

29:05.110 --> 29:05.810
Iced treats.

29:06.640 --> 29:07.540
Opening up to each other.

29:08.830 --> 29:10.090
Promising to stay together forever.

29:11.680 --> 29:12.500
Those were your memories

29:12.500 --> 29:13.890
with Lu Wuyi.

29:14.960 --> 29:16.060
But now they're happening

29:16.060 --> 29:17.170
between you and Su Jian.

29:18.780 --> 29:20.500
Maybe the memories in that painting

29:22.680 --> 29:23.540
are fake.

29:23.590 --> 29:24.460
True or false,

29:25.070 --> 29:26.540
we'll find out once we ask Han Ba.

29:29.000 --> 29:30.330
But I'd rather believe

29:31.350 --> 29:33.090
your story with Lu Wuyi

29:33.640 --> 29:35.130
was fabricated by Jiu Ying.

29:36.200 --> 29:37.540
Not just the memories,

29:38.720 --> 29:39.940
even Lu Wuyi herself

29:41.160 --> 29:42.260
may have been made up.

29:45.270 --> 29:46.980
She stole the manuscript

29:49.000 --> 29:50.650
because she didn't want you to find out the truth.

29:52.310 --> 29:53.940
But Ji Ling said they were together.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.220
Ji Ling is defending her.

30:11.200 --> 30:11.740
Wu,

30:12.720 --> 30:13.610
I know it's you.

30:14.550 --> 30:15.890
The only one who could withstand

30:15.960 --> 30:17.370
Wu Shiguang and Han Ba's power

30:18.550 --> 30:19.330
is you.

30:20.680 --> 30:21.410
But

30:22.070 --> 30:23.980
they never attacked you before.

30:24.680 --> 30:26.890
When did you absorb their power?

30:27.110 --> 30:27.610
Wuyi.

30:29.110 --> 30:29.700
Wuyi.

30:31.720 --> 30:32.370
Ji,

30:33.440 --> 30:34.060
help me.

30:36.790 --> 30:37.610
I'm begging you.

30:44.030 --> 30:45.650
I didn't give you away to Wu Wangyan.

30:46.160 --> 30:47.410
So, will you tell me

30:48.310 --> 30:49.570
what's really going on?

30:52.830 --> 30:53.460
Wu.

31:02.030 --> 31:02.650
Wu.

31:04.440 --> 31:05.810
Tell me the truth.

31:28.200 --> 31:28.940
Backlash...

31:31.070 --> 31:32.060
Your Word Magic

31:32.720 --> 31:34.220
is stronger than Xiaowei's?

31:36.110 --> 31:36.700
Wu,

31:38.440 --> 31:40.170
what happened to you?

31:41.310 --> 31:42.160
Why did you

31:42.160 --> 31:43.700
use Word Magic on Mu Long?

31:53.000 --> 31:54.650
Why did you take those manuscript pages?

31:56.830 --> 31:57.570
If you won't speak,

31:59.200 --> 32:00.330
I'll ask Wu Wangyan.

32:01.830 --> 32:02.410
Don't!

32:14.790 --> 32:15.780
Those pages

32:20.310 --> 32:21.460
contain a secret

32:22.030 --> 32:23.850
I never wanted Wangyan to know.

32:26.750 --> 32:28.540
I would lose her.

32:31.880 --> 32:32.780
What secret?

32:38.110 --> 32:40.130
I'm not a fox from the Formless Moon Sect.

32:45.750 --> 32:46.740
I'm not even

32:50.490 --> 32:51.610
a demon.

32:54.000 --> 32:55.170
I'm a monster.

32:55.260 --> 32:58.020
♪How should this story be told...♪

32:58.680 --> 33:00.940
I'm a piece of trash

33:04.920 --> 33:05.700
stitched together by Jiu Ying.

33:08.590 --> 33:10.060
I learned that all my memories

33:10.960 --> 33:12.310
are fake

33:12.310 --> 33:13.260
from Mu Long's story.

33:16.720 --> 33:17.460
So

33:18.920 --> 33:20.370
I went to confront Jiu Ying.

33:21.960 --> 33:22.570
Jiu Ying,

33:23.190 --> 33:24.080
come out.

33:27.260 --> 33:29.900
♪How do you measure memory♪

33:30.180 --> 33:35.020
♪To cut the past into clothes to wear?♪

33:35.130 --> 33:36.160
Why

33:37.550 --> 33:39.330
do my memories with Wangyan

33:39.920 --> 33:41.740
appear in Mu Long's story?

33:43.720 --> 33:44.410
Why

33:45.720 --> 33:47.740
are Little Pomegranate and Wangyan's stories

33:48.720 --> 33:50.200
exactly the same

33:50.200 --> 33:50.980
as mine?

33:52.180 --> 33:53.180
♪Don't be afraid...♪

33:53.200 --> 33:53.980
Just why?

33:56.680 --> 33:58.060
What did you do

33:59.440 --> 34:01.090
to my memories?

34:04.180 --> 34:07.580
♪You brave the wind and bear the rain♪

34:08.100 --> 34:14.900
♪Thank you for the shelter of your shade♪

34:16.220 --> 34:19.740
♪Moon sets, crows cry♪

34:20.130 --> 34:23.620
♪Time slips by, a swift steed in flight...♪

34:23.800 --> 34:26.690
When the Formless Moon Sect attacked the flood dragons,

34:27.360 --> 34:28.980
they fell into the trap of Xie Lingxi

34:30.000 --> 34:31.290
and were completely wiped out.

34:34.110 --> 34:35.380
Before they were reborn,

34:36.280 --> 34:38.420
Jiu Ying took a part

34:39.390 --> 34:41.500
from each of their bodies,

34:42.510 --> 34:43.770
flesh, veins, spirit, or qi,

34:46.030 --> 34:46.900
and stitched them together

34:49.190 --> 34:50.460
to create me.

34:55.320 --> 34:57.650
And what she took from Wangyan

35:01.510 --> 35:02.380
was her heart.

35:04.110 --> 35:04.820
What about you?

35:09.510 --> 35:10.290
Where is your heart?

35:13.320 --> 35:14.210
That explains

35:16.070 --> 35:17.570
why Wu Wangyan dotes on you so much.

35:20.280 --> 35:21.060
That's because

35:22.800 --> 35:23.900
you are her heart.

35:27.920 --> 35:29.900
But Jiu Ying placed a spirit fragment

35:30.440 --> 35:32.060
in her heart.

35:41.110 --> 35:43.130
The last fragment you've been searching for

35:48.480 --> 35:49.460
is with me.

36:13.800 --> 36:14.940
I knew it all along.

36:19.550 --> 36:20.460
I just

36:22.360 --> 36:23.610
didn't understand

36:26.150 --> 36:28.170
why you stayed by my side,

36:30.230 --> 36:32.210
yet I couldn't sense that last fragment.

36:33.630 --> 36:34.290
Turns out

36:35.630 --> 36:37.570
it was hidden in Wangyan's heart.

36:38.960 --> 36:39.980
Her heart

36:42.480 --> 36:43.690
has always been protecting you.

36:45.400 --> 36:46.380
Wangyan's heart...

36:49.070 --> 36:50.090
When our hearts

36:50.760 --> 36:52.420
come into this world,

36:53.480 --> 36:54.570
one way or another,

36:55.320 --> 36:57.170
they are bound to be marked by love.

36:58.920 --> 36:59.540
Love

37:01.000 --> 37:03.610
is the oldest

37:05.550 --> 37:07.090
and the most powerful spell of all.

37:11.840 --> 37:13.210
Before any of us were revived,

37:13.210 --> 37:14.290
Jiu Ying

37:15.840 --> 37:17.500
altered our memories.

37:24.000 --> 37:24.650
Wangyan.

37:25.840 --> 37:27.610
Wangyan, you made iced treats again.

38:01.840 --> 38:02.540
Wangyan.

38:03.550 --> 38:04.130
Let's go.

38:11.230 --> 38:12.730
You always manage to find me.

38:13.190 --> 38:15.060
You always hide in the dark.

38:15.320 --> 38:16.310
Of course no one else

38:16.310 --> 38:17.290
can see you.

38:18.360 --> 38:19.380
But I can.

38:20.400 --> 38:21.130
My heart

38:21.960 --> 38:23.610
can feel you're here.

38:45.710 --> 38:47.380
Xie Lingxi killed all of you.

38:48.230 --> 38:49.290
But he didn't know

38:49.880 --> 38:51.020
the Power of the Moon

38:51.800 --> 38:53.090
is eternal.

39:04.550 --> 39:06.090
When everyone was reborn,

39:06.760 --> 39:08.690
they took those altered memories

39:09.190 --> 39:10.130
as truth.

39:11.960 --> 39:12.940
They believed

39:12.940 --> 39:13.980
they had a younger sister like me.

39:20.440 --> 39:21.650
I used to think

39:21.920 --> 39:23.020
I was the new moon,

39:24.230 --> 39:25.650
one of the moon phases.

39:27.630 --> 39:29.130
But in the end,

39:33.550 --> 39:34.730
I was never real.

39:38.590 --> 39:40.690
I'm nothing but a shameless thief.

39:43.360 --> 39:45.250
I stole their memories

39:47.110 --> 39:48.540
to piece together a life of my own.

39:52.920 --> 39:53.500
Full moon,

39:55.760 --> 39:56.340
waning gibbous,

39:57.440 --> 39:58.170
last-quarter,

40:00.070 --> 40:00.730
waxing gibbous,

40:01.760 --> 40:02.650
first-quarter,

40:03.840 --> 40:04.500
waning crescent,

40:05.880 --> 40:06.650
and waxing crescent.

40:08.320 --> 40:09.340
In the sky,

40:14.230 --> 40:15.980
there was never a place for me.

40:38.510 --> 40:39.610
Your place

40:41.630 --> 40:42.650
was never in the sky.

40:45.880 --> 40:46.860
It's in my heart.

40:49.780 --> 40:52.100
♪We count down to tomorrow...♪

40:53.630 --> 40:55.130
Nothing between us

40:56.710 --> 40:57.900
is fake.

40:59.590 --> 41:01.380
From the day we met,

41:03.880 --> 41:06.130
every moment this world has witnessed

41:09.230 --> 41:11.060
belongs only to us.

41:12.140 --> 41:14.660
♪Let's go back in time♪

41:15.020 --> 41:17.300
♪Snow piled high by the window♪

41:17.380 --> 41:20.660
♪Under sparks of fireworks, we♪

41:20.780 --> 41:22.980
♪Smiled through tears so sweet♪

41:23.100 --> 41:26.180
♪You said you'd find a little corner♪

41:26.220 --> 41:28.500
♪And give me ten thousand wildflowers♪

41:28.540 --> 41:34.420
♪Softly telling me you'd stay with me forever♪

41:34.660 --> 41:37.340
♪Under the world's small roof♪

41:38.100 --> 41:41.100
♪You're right here by my side...♪

41:45.230 --> 41:47.380
But how did Wuyi come to know all this?

41:49.960 --> 41:51.940
She arrived at the inn at the same time as us.

41:52.760 --> 41:54.210
How did you learn

41:55.710 --> 41:57.130
the truth?

42:00.880 --> 42:02.060
Maybe

42:03.920 --> 42:05.940
Lu Wuyi went through something we don't know about.

42:10.190 --> 42:10.860
Wu,

42:12.840 --> 42:13.540
tell me.

42:15.230 --> 42:16.380
No matter what happens,

42:18.000 --> 42:19.940
I'll face it with you.

42:23.920 --> 42:24.880
This isn't the first time

42:24.880 --> 42:26.340
I've been through this.

42:27.760 --> 42:28.980
The Yanbi Inn.

42:30.400 --> 42:31.540
This drought.

42:32.960 --> 42:34.130
It's not the first time,

42:35.510 --> 42:36.730
not the tenth,

42:38.360 --> 42:39.690
but countless times.

42:54.360 --> 42:55.980
From the moment we entered the inn,

42:56.000 --> 42:57.290
at the Zi hour that night,

42:58.070 --> 42:59.610
I've been trapped in a loop,

43:00.590 --> 43:01.940
reliving it over and over again.

43:05.540 --> 43:12.500
[First rewind]

43:53.000 --> 43:56.020
Big drumstick...

43:58.000 --> 43:58.650
Miss Mu.

44:00.880 --> 44:02.250
- Miss Mu. - What are you trying to do?

44:02.800 --> 44:03.170
You...

44:03.360 --> 44:05.130
You've stained my manuscript.

44:44.920 --> 44:46.770
I've relived everything again and again.

44:47.840 --> 44:49.340
I've endured countless attacks from Han Ba,

44:49.670 --> 44:50.500
Wu Shiguang,

44:50.960 --> 44:52.940
and Li Jie.

44:53.710 --> 44:54.960
That's why none of their spells

44:54.960 --> 44:55.900
can harm me.

44:56.960 --> 44:58.130
And my Word Magic

44:59.320 --> 45:00.460
has surpassed yours.

45:03.190 --> 45:04.460
Time reversal?

45:06.630 --> 45:08.570
How could Jiu Ying possess such power?

45:11.000 --> 45:11.940
I don't know.

45:18.630 --> 45:19.860
Time reversal

45:20.760 --> 45:22.540
damages the body,

45:23.230 --> 45:23.770
doesn't it?

45:25.510 --> 45:26.020
Yes.

45:28.320 --> 45:29.940
And the toll only gets worse each time.

45:34.760 --> 45:35.420
So

45:36.030 --> 45:36.820
Ji,

45:37.400 --> 45:38.170
help me.

45:40.400 --> 45:41.340
I'm afraid.

45:42.230 --> 45:44.090
I'm afraid that once Wangyan finds out the truth,

45:44.960 --> 45:45.900
she'll hate me.

45:47.030 --> 45:48.460
I don't want to lose her.

45:50.190 --> 45:50.820
Don't be afraid.

45:52.230 --> 45:53.860
You stole the manuscript

45:54.960 --> 45:56.650
and used Word Magic on Mu Long.

45:57.800 --> 45:59.420
Wangyan will never find out what happened.

46:03.070 --> 46:03.540
No.

46:04.760 --> 46:05.980
There's another way.

46:08.190 --> 46:09.770
All the truth and memories

46:10.000 --> 46:11.980
are stored inside Mu Long's horn pendant.

46:12.710 --> 46:14.250
Every time time reverses,

46:15.030 --> 46:16.280
I can't stop Wangyan

46:16.280 --> 46:17.730
from discovering what's inside.

46:19.110 --> 46:20.020
Maybe

46:22.000 --> 46:24.380
that's why I'm trapped here.

46:26.480 --> 46:28.570
My fear of losing her

46:30.800 --> 46:32.020
has bound me to this place.

46:35.280 --> 46:36.340
But this time,

46:38.400 --> 46:39.570
I know the truth.

46:41.190 --> 46:42.650
Maybe this is fate.

46:44.280 --> 46:46.090
It's giving me a chance to change everything for you.

46:50.280 --> 46:51.380
You're willing to help me?

46:55.710 --> 46:57.650
I would do anything for you.

47:01.960 --> 47:04.020
Take that pendant back for me.

47:05.590 --> 47:06.500
Help me.

47:50.500 --> 47:55.900
♪The wind blows by, and memories sway with dreams♪

47:56.580 --> 48:02.580
♪I stay silent, afraid the fire in my heart will rise♪

48:03.460 --> 48:06.100
♪Reed flowers sway with burning heat♪

48:06.780 --> 48:09.580
♪Shaking the story into something blurred and worn♪

48:10.220 --> 48:15.460
♪I am only a murmuring traveler through wind and snow♪

48:17.180 --> 48:22.900
♪Watching the evening glow turn cold and fade into night♪

48:23.460 --> 48:29.500
♪Watching every stroke and mark spell out reluctance♪

48:30.180 --> 48:33.460
♪Watching spider lilies bloom across the hills♪

48:34.100 --> 48:37.060
♪Watching the one in my dreams send back bitterness♪

48:37.620 --> 48:42.700
♪Watching the corner of your lips stained with a touch of dark crimson♪

48:44.300 --> 48:50.060
♪From now on, you'll never grow old♪

48:50.660 --> 48:56.100
♪Even with earth between us, I'll softly sing with you♪

48:57.980 --> 49:00.940
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you♪

49:01.460 --> 49:04.420
♪In winter, I'll boil snow to warm the fading dusk♪

49:04.940 --> 49:10.140
♪Of joy and sorrow, of countless softly lit homes, I'll speak to you♪

49:10.660 --> 49:16.700
♪Brewing the years into a daydream impossible to wake from♪

49:17.300 --> 49:23.540
♪Draining every joy and sorrow, crushing the void within the heart♪

49:24.020 --> 49:32.340
♪With white hair and dewy eyes, I sigh for youth, when words defied the heart♪

49:32.940 --> 49:39.740
♪Whose dream lies buried beneath the cenotaph?♪
